00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,750
I missed you.

261
00:20:11,055 --> 00:20:14,422
I know that I called you
a toddler and all that...

262
00:20:14,445 --> 00:20:15,752
But, er...

263
00:20:17,708 --> 00:20:18,953
you're my toddler.

264
00:20:19,819 --> 00:20:21,408
What I actually wanted to...

265
00:20:22,858 --> 00:20:24,482
How did you get that cold sore?

266
00:20:26,435 --> 00:20:28,625
You kissed someone else!
- I didn't!

267
00:20:28,638 --> 00:20:30,778
Are you mimicing my dad?
- No, Mary, wait!

268
00:20:34,352 --> 00:20:35,185
Look...

269
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:39,793
Today was the first day at school without
you, and it was the worst day ever.

270
00:20:40,199 --> 00:20:40,983
Really.

271
00:20:40,990 --> 00:20:42,671
Is that salmon on your hand?

272
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:46,273
Shit, I'm sorry.
Your allergies, I'm so sorry.

273
00:20:54,762 --> 00:20:56,609
Hey, guys.

274
00:20:56,905 --> 00:20:58,232
Wanna buy a bike?

275
00:20:58,488 --> 00:21:01,203
Tony, what is this?
That's my bike.

276
00:21:01,253 --> 00:21:03,293
No way, it's mine.

277
00:21:04,643 --> 00:21:06,367
But for five euros, it's yours.

278
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,213
Five euros?

279
00:21:08,791 --> 00:21:12,481
I don't have that. I spend it
all on your birthday treats.

280
00:21:13,775 --> 00:21:14,684
What?

281
00:21:14,807 --> 00:21:15,778
Five euros?

282
00:21:18,323 --> 00:21:19,348
Here you go.

283
00:21:27,476 --> 00:21:30,115
You like it like that, right?
I saw you in art class.

284
00:21:30,164 --> 00:21:31,720
Yeah, they like that.

285
00:21:40,748 --> 00:21:41,581
Tim?

286
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,473
Yeah?

287
00:21:43,884 --> 00:21:45,240
Is this your backpack?

288
00:21:49,233 --> 00:21:50,223
Yup.

289
00:21:53,075 --> 00:21:54,195
Thank you, Eddy.

290
00:21:57,929 --> 00:21:58,965
Hey guys.

291
00:21:59,316 --> 00:22:02,212
This is Comfort. She's new here.
I'm showing her around.

292
00:22:02,735 --> 00:22:04,540
Hi Comfort.

293
00:22:04,826 --> 00:22:08,233
I don't think she speaks Dutch.
She's from Thailand.

294
00:22:23,203 --> 00:22:24,323
For you.

295
00:23:01,468 --> 00:23:02,432
Hey, Lars.

296
00:23:03,485 --> 00:23:05,293
No Viktor, not now please.

297
00:23:05,958 --> 00:23:08,823
Hold on, I think you'll like this.
- No, Viktor!

298
00:23:08,847 --> 00:23:12,455
I'm done with you!
Get lost! That's enough!

299
00:23:17,944 --> 00:23:19,528
Sorry Lars, about everything.

300
00:23:21,745 --> 00:23:23,011
I feel you.

301
00:23:23,607 --> 00:23:24,685
I feel...

